description: AMUNDI MSCI EM LATIN AMERICA UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Emerging Markets Latam Index, net dividends reinvested (Net Return), calculated in US Dollars and converted in EURO, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the leading stocks from Latin American equity emerging markets, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI EM Latin America UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
